description: Проверяет, что при запросе списка заказов по id курьера  в ответе возвращаются все завершенные заказы этого курьера

steps.name: Send POST request to create a courier to api/v1/courier
Send POST request for authorization of the courier to /api/v1/courier/login
Send POST request to create an order to /api/v1/orders
Send GET request to receive an order by its track to /api/v1/orders/track
Send PUT request to accept an order to /api/v1/orders/accept/:id
Send PUT request to finish an order to /api/v1/orders/finish/:id
Send GET request to receive a list of orders by courier id to /api/v1/orders
Send DELETE request to remove the courier to api/v1/courier/:id
